graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack K8s Operator"
        Controller[LlamaStackDistribution Controller<br/>Reconciliation Engine]
        ClusterInfo[Cluster Info Manager<br/>Config & Images]
        Kustomizer[Kustomizer<br/>Manifest Renderer]
        ResourceHelper[Resource Helper<br/>K8s Resource Builder]
        NetworkPolicy[Network Policy Manager<br/>Feature-Flagged]
        CABundle[CA Bundle Manager<br/>TLS Config]
        Metrics[Metrics Exporter<br/>:8443]
        Health[Health Probe Handler<br/>:8081]

        Controller -->|uses| ClusterInfo
        Controller -->|renders manifests| Kustomizer
        Controller -->|builds resources| ResourceHelper
        Controller -->|creates if enabled| NetworkPolicy
        Controller -->|manages TLS| CABundle
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
        Controller -->|provides| Health
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        LlamaStackCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR<br/>llamastack.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        Deployment[Deployment<br/>Llama Stack Server]
        Service[ClusterIP Service<br/>:8321]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Model Storage]
        SA[ServiceAccount<br/>instance-name-sa]
        HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler<br/>Auto-scaling]
        PDB[PodDisruptionBudget<br/>HA Protection]
        NP[NetworkPolicy<br/>Ingress Control]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        Registry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io/docker.io]
        vLLM[vLLM Inference<br/>8000/TCP HTTP]
        Ollama[Ollama Inference<br/>11434/TCP HTTP]
        HF[HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Management]
        TrustedCA[ODH Trusted CA Bundle<br/>ConfigMap]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Metadata Service]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| LlamaStackCR
    Dashboard -->|creates via UI| LlamaStackCR

    LlamaStackCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates/manages| Deployment
    Controller -->|creates/manages| Service
    Controller -->|creates/manages| PVC
    Controller -->|creates/manages| SA
    Controller -->|creates/manages| HPA
    Controller -->|creates/manages| PDB
    Controller -->|creates if enabled| NP

    Controller -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI
    Controller -->|auto-detects| TrustedCA

    Deployment -->|pulls images| Registry
    Deployment -->|calls| vLLM
    Deployment -->|calls| Ollama
    Deployment -->|downloads models| HF
    Deployment -->|queries metadata| ModelRegistry

    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>ServiceMonitor]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style LlamaStackCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Deployment fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style vLLM fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Ollama fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style HF fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#b8e986,stroke:#333
    style TrustedCA fill:#b8e986,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#b8e986,stroke:#333
